    {
      "title": "<span id=\"#25887\" class=\"scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold flex items-center\"><h1 class=\"inline !mb-1 scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold\">emphasise</h1><div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\">(v.)</div></span>",
      "html": "<p>主要用于英国英语的拼写方式，与 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of emphasize \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/emphasize\">emphasize</a> 相同； 有关拼写，请参见 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of -ize \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/-ize\">-ize</a>。相关词汇： <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">Emphasised</i>； <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">emphasising</i>。</p>"
    }
